## ⏱ Complexity

| Type  | Complexity |
| ----- | ---------- |
| Time  | O(n)       |
| Space | O(n)       |

---

## ⚡ Key Points

* Always think **bijection (two-way mapping)**
* One map alone is **not enough**
* Order of characters matters
* Works best with **HashMap**

---

## 🚀 Learnings

* This is a classic **mapping consistency problem**
* Similar problems:

  * Pattern matching
  * Word pattern
* Trick: Whenever you see **"one-to-one mapping" → use 2 maps**

